      • propertyChange

        public void propertyChange(utility.observer.event.ObserverEvent<java.lang.Object,java.lang.Object> event)
        Implements switch, takes name of the event and calls methods in BookModel or RequestModel, depending on event name. If the name is "BOOKLIST", calls setBookList() method in BookModel. If the name is "REQUEST", calls setRequests() method in RequestModel. If the name is "REQUEST UPDATE", calls setRequests() method in RequestModel. If the nameis "LOCAL USER", calls setLocalUser() in the StudentModel.
